	  (suggested by Kenji Nishishiro)
	* ext/ooi8/oraconf.rb: support Oracle Instant Installer.
	  (suggested by Eustaquio Rangel de Oliveira Jr.)
	* Makefile, ext/oci8/extconf.rb: change version to 0.1.9

